'''德克兰·希尔'''是一名记者、学者及顾问，也是研究国际体坛关于[[假球|假球]]及[[贪污|贪污]]问题的知名专家。他于2008年，作为 Chevening 学者，得到牛津大学的社会学博士学位。他的书＂The Fix: Organized Crime and Soccer＂已经被翻译成十五种语言。该书概述了赌博市场全球化对国际体坛所带来的新危机，其中包括对职业足球可能存在的操控。他也是一名Global Integrity评论家，并深入探讨过俄罗斯黑手党对专业冰上曲棍球的影响。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://goal.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/11/27/q-a-on-match-fixing-with-declan-hill-author-of-the-fix |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2011-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110703073546/http://goal.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/11/27/q-a-on-match-fixing-with-declan-hill-author-of-the-fix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://pitchinvasion.net/blog/2011/05/11/fifas-half-hearted-fight-against-corruption-continues-its-tepid-march |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110625132732/http://pitchinvasion.net/blog/2011/05/11/fifas-half-hearted-fight-against-corruption-continues-its-tepid-march/ |archivedate=2011-06-25 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/0,1518,575586,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2012-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120515201240/http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/0,1518,575586,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>["Declan Hill "The Fix" match fixing interview". SoccerPro.com. Retrieved 2009-01-30]</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sociology.ox.ac.uk/index.php/publications/graduate-books.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930094554/http://www.sociology.ox.ac.uk/index.php/publications/graduate-books.html |archivedate=2011-09-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.britishcouncil.org/british-council-canada-newsletter-spring-2010.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-19  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010090013/http://www.britishcouncil.org/british-council-canada-newsletter-spring-2010.pdf |archivedate=2012-10-10 }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite web 