== 早年 ==
希尔毕业于加拿大国家戏剧学校、[[多伦多大学三一学院|多伦多大学三一学院]]和牛津大学；曾在逸夫节及加拿大各剧院饰演过一些小角色，并在印度参与Doordshan电视系列的Bhaarat ek Khoj 演出。由于在加尔各答大街诊所的经验，他逐渐从戏剧界转入新闻界。希尔曾在加拿大广播公司（CBC）任职，最初是担任其最知名节目"The fifth estate"的调查记者，然后担任Newsworld International的主持人。他的节目和文章也曾在BBC Radio World Service，BBC 4频道（Guardian），Sunday Telegraph (（伦敦），及各种国际性新闻媒体渠道播出过。<ref>[http://www.entnts.ca/en/alumni/all/acting/1980.aspx]{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Trinity_College_(Canada)_alumni |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2011-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113005943/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Trinity_College_(Canada)_alumni |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref>[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2430852/filmoyear]</ref> <ref>[http://books.google.ca/books?id=5pNe8rtCZ_MC&pg=PA71&lpg=PA71&dq=%22declan+Hill%22+%22James+orbinski%22&source=bl&ots=D6dUYm1HJH&sig=hJb4DeOQ1eOimJZt6dnIrRgGDQI&hl=en&ei=fNPSTcq_CdTPiALbucDTCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBgQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false]</ref><ref>[http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:pUVKTMKtm-sJ]</ref><ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/viewpoint/vp_hill/20040608.html+%22declan+Hill%22+%22fifth+estate%22&cd=2&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=ca&client=safari&source=www.google.ca]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2001/08/25/airtransat_010825.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2012-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109161106/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2001/08/25/airtransat_010825.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.straight.com/article-330896/vancouver/author-declan-hill-investigates-problem-fixing-soccer-matches |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2010-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100827152519/http://www.straight.com/article-330896/vancouver/author-declan-hill-investigates-problem-fixing-soccer-matches |dead-ur